</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Game =E2=80=A6=C2=A0used? Used for what? The p=
atch says =E2=80=9CMLB Debut,=E2=80=9D you stick it on your jersey, you pla=
y a game, you take it off your jersey, you sell it. (Well, Topps sells it.)=
 The patch does not=C2=A0do anything. It is not a piece of sporting apparat=
us. It is not quite an ad either; it is the ex nihilo creation of a collect=
ible. =E2=80=9CGet=C2=A0<a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/=
click/31011090.260442/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cubnl0aW1lcy5jb20vMjAyMy8wMy8yNi9zcG9yd=
HMvYmFzZWJhbGwvYW50aG9ueS12b2xwZS15YW5rZWVzLmh0bWw_Y2FtcGFpZ25faWQ9MjM4JmVt=
